ğŸ‘¤ Get Users (No Authentication Required)
GET /users


This endpoint returns a list of dummy users.

ğŸ“¦ Get Products (Authentication Required)
GET /products


This endpoint requires authentication.

ğŸ” Authentication Setup

In your API testing tool:

Header Key: Authorization

Header Value:

Bearer mysecrettoken


If the token is missing or incorrect, access will be denied.

ğŸ² Random Name & Quote (No Authentication Required)
GET /random


Response Example:

{
  "randomName": "Jordan",
  "randomQuote": "Consistency beats talent"
}


Refreshing or calling this endpoint again will return a different random name and quote.

